#: ../../reference/micropython2_migration.rst:4
msgid "MicroPython 2.0 Migration Guide"
msgstr "MicroPython 2.0迁移指南"

#: ../../reference/micropython2_migration.rst:6
msgid ""
"MicroPython 2.0 is the (currently in development, not yet available) next"
" major release of MicroPython."
msgstr "MicroPython 2.0是MicroPython的下一个主要版本(目前正在开发中，尚未可用)。"

#: ../../reference/micropython2_migration.rst:9
msgid ""
"After maintaining API compatibility for almost a decade with the ``1.x`` "
"series, in order to unblock some project-wide improvements MicroPython "
"2.0 will introduce a small number of breaking API changes that will "
"require some programs to be updated. This guide explains how to update "
"your Python code to accommodate these changes."
msgstr ""
"在与 ``1.x`` 系列维护了近十年的API兼容性之后。为了支持一些项目范围内的改进，MicroPython "
"2.0将引入少量破坏性的API更改，这将需要更新一些程序。本指南解释了如何更新Python代码以适应这些更改。"

#: ../../reference/micropython2_migration.rst:15
msgid ""
"This document is a work-in-progress. As more work is done on MicroPython "
"2.0, more items will be added to the lists below."
msgstr "这份文件是一份正在进行的工作。随着MicroPython 2.0上的更多工作完成，更多的项目将被添加到下面的列表中。"

#: ../../reference/micropython2_migration.rst:18
msgid ""
"**Note:** There are currently no MicroPython 2.0 firmware builds "
"available for download. You can build it yourself by enabling the "
"``MICROPY_PREVIEW_VERSION_2`` config option. As it gets closer to being "
"ready for release, builds will be provided for both ``1.x.y`` and "
"``2.0.0-preview``."
msgstr ""
"**注意：** 目前没有MicroPython 2.0固件版本可供下载。您可以通过启用 ``MICROPY_PREVIEW_VERSION_2``"
" 配置选项来自己构建它。随着它即将准备发布，我们将同时为 ``1.x.y`` 和 ``2.0.0预览版`` 提供构建版本。"

#: ../../reference/micropython2_migration.rst:24
msgid "Hardware and peripherals"
msgstr "硬件和外围设备"

#: ../../reference/micropython2_migration.rst:27
#: ../../reference/micropython2_migration.rst:44
#: ../../reference/micropython2_migration.rst:62
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "概述"

#: ../../reference/micropython2_migration.rst:29
msgid ""
"The goal is to improve consistency in the :mod:`machine` APIs across "
"different ports, making it easier to write code, documentation, and "
"tutorials that work on any supported microcontroller."
msgstr "目标是提高 :mod:`machine` API跨不同移植版本的一致性，使其更容易编写在任何支持的微控制器上工作的代码，文档和教程。"

#: ../../reference/micropython2_migration.rst:33
msgid "This means that some ports' APIs need to change to match other ports."
msgstr "这意味着一些移植版本的API需要更改以匹配其他移植版本。"

#: ../../reference/micropython2_migration.rst:36
#: ../../reference/micropython2_migration.rst:54
#: ../../reference/micropython2_migration.rst:72
msgid "Changes"
msgstr "改变"

#: ../../reference/micropython2_migration.rst:38
#: ../../reference/micropython2_migration.rst:56
msgid "*None yet*"
msgstr "*暂无*"

#: ../../reference/micropython2_migration.rst:41
msgid "OS & filesystem"
msgstr "操作系统和文件系统"

#: ../../reference/micropython2_migration.rst:46
msgid ""
"The primary goal is to support the ability to execute :term:`.mpy files "
"<.mpy file>` directly from the filesystem without first copying them into"
" RAM. This improves code deployment time and reduces memory overhead and "
"fragmentation."
msgstr ""
"主要目标是支持直接从文件系统执行 :term:`.mpy files <.mpy "
"file>`，而不首先将它们复制到RAM中。这改善了代码部署时间，减少了内存开销和碎片。"

#: ../../reference/micropython2_migration.rst:50
msgid ""
"Additionally, a further goal is to support a more flexible way of "
"configuring partitions, filesystem types, and options like USB mass "
"storage."
msgstr "此外，进一步的目标是支持更灵活的方式来配置分区、文件系统类型和USB大容量存储等选项。"

#: ../../reference/micropython2_migration.rst:59
msgid "CPython compatibility"
msgstr "CPython 兼容性"

#: ../../reference/micropython2_migration.rst:64
msgid ""
"The goal is to improve compatibility with CPython by removing MicroPython"
" extensions from CPython APIs. In most cases this means moving existing "
"MicroPython-specific functions or classes to new modules."
msgstr ""
"目标是通过从CPython "
"API中删除MicroPython扩展来改善与CPython的兼容性。在大多数情况下，这意味着将现有的特定于micropython的函数或类移动到新的模块中。"

#: ../../reference/micropython2_migration.rst:68
msgid ""
"This makes it easier to write code that works on both CPython and "
"MicroPython, which is useful for development and testing."
msgstr "这使得编写在CPython和MicroPython上都能工作的代码变得更容易，这对开发和测试很有用。"

#: ../../reference/micropython2_migration.rst:74
msgid ""
"Introduction of a new module :mod:`vfs`.  The following functions and "
"classes have moved out of :mod:`os` to :mod:`vfs`: - `os.mount` - "
"`os.umount` - `os.VfsFat` - `os.VfsLfs1` - `os.VfsLfs2` - `os.VfsPosix`"
msgstr ""
"引入了新的模块 :mod:`vfs`.  以下函数和类已从 :mod:`os` 移动到 :mod:`vfs`: - `os.mount` - "
"`os.umount` - `os.VfsFat` - `os.VfsLfs1` - `os.VfsLfs2` - `os.VfsPosix`"
